The paper discusses a cloud-based data management and analytics framework that provides secure and scalable storage and analysis of large datasets. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Databases (cs.DB), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Software Engineering (cs.SE). However, given the focus on distributed data management and analytics, cs.DC is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.CR for the emphasis on security.
